        <item>
            <title>破格无后车窗设计，北欧简约风 Polestar 4 轿跑香港试驾</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/05/hk-polestar-4-testdrive/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hk-polestar-4-testdrive</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/05/hk-polestar-4-testdrive/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 05:08:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[polestar]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[polestar 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Volvo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[北欧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[霤神之槌]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288454</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>越来越多国产电动车登场，要在香港取得一席位绝不容易。Polestar 最近在香港推出第二款 SUV Coupe 电动车 Polestar 4，结合跑车美学与 SUV 宽敞实用性，独特的无后窗设计相更令不少人眼前一亮，以下就为大家带来详细介绍！</p><h3>无后车窗源自设计、空间和科技</h3><p>主打高性能及豪华车箱的 Polestar 4 最抢眼之处肯定是它大胆且创新的无后车窗设计，其背后的原因主要围绕设计、空间优化以及科技应用方面。取消传统后车窗可以让车尾更加流畅和简洁，减少气流扰动，进一步优化车辆的空气动力学性能，从而提高效率并延长电池续航里程。另外，无后车窗的设计让 C 柱到车尾的结构更加完整，提升了车身刚性，同时腾出更多车内空间，尤其是后排座椅的头部空间更加宽敞，而全景天窗也好好地弥补传统后车窗带来的采光功能，提供更现代化乘坐体验。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_113847-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_113847-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_113847-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289617" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114127-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114127-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114127.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲从后面看尾部看似仍保留了后车窗设计，不过它只是金属尾门的一部份，并不透光。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_115957-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_115957-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_115957.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120141-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120141-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120141.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲特大的全景天幕令没有后窗的 Polestar 4 感觉仍然相当开扬。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114644-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114644-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114644.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p style="text-align: center;">▲当打开尾门及翻下后排座位便可以打通整个后座及车尾箱。</p><h3>后置镜头提供更广阔视野</h3><p>取代后车窗的是数码后视镜系统，该系统由后置摄像头和屏幕组成，提供比传统后车窗更广、更清晰的后方视野。数位后视镜不受后排乘客、行李或夜间低光环境的影响，让驾驶者的视野始终保持清晰。这种技术还代表了 Polestar 对科技与设计融合的追求，为驾驶者提供未来感的驾驶体验。无后车窗设计符合 Polestar 一贯追求的极简主义与未来感设计语言，让整辆车看起来更具雕塑感和视觉冲击。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114439-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114439-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114439-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114439.jpg 1920w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这个后视镜头可以把即时画面传送到倒后镜上显示</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_122649-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_122649-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_122649.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120207-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120207-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120207.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲虽然没有四门均不设窗框，但 Polestar 4 的隔音效果却非常出色。</p><h3>流线车身风阻更低辨识率更高</h3><p>除了无段后车窗设计之外，Polestar 4 的车身外观以流线型设计为主，展现出跑车般的优雅比例，并融入多项空气动力学优化，例如隐藏式门把手和精致的车身线条，有效减少风阻，提升效率。车头设计采用封闭式格栅，搭配独特的 「Thor’s Hammer」 LED 日间行车灯，展现出品牌辨识度极高的未来感，此外车尾采用了贯穿式 LED 灯条，让车辆在夜间更具辨识度，同时强调车身的宽度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120620-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120620-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120620.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289618" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114013-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114013-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114013.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Polestar 4 也拥有家族式的「雷神之槌」头灯，辨识率极高。</p><h3></h3><h3>短评:，电子后镜欠立体感、驾驶者需时适应</h3><p>在实际试车后，小编认为无后窗设计一定需要时间适应，因为数码后镜失去了传统物理倒后镜的立体感，引致看起来较难确定后方车辆的距离，在观塘道一带繁忙路段试驾时也需要保持较远距离才能确保安全切线，对于在路面常看后镜确保没有「拉龙」的驾驶者相信更能体会新设计的不同。小记最深刻的体会是在飞鹅山脚一段较窄的路段由于「冧树」需要原路后退约 80 米，全程只靠没有立体感的电子后镜非常不习惯，小编需要多次使用两旁侧镜及直接伸头望出车外确认两旁路旁距离，可见没有后窗对于习惯旧式驾驶方法的老一辈司机需要较多时间适应。相反，在泊车方面由于近年已经习惯使用后镜头和泊车雷达等辅助驾驶功能，在试泊 S 位和 L 位基本上都没有任何难度可以即时上手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289621" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_122527-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_122527-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_122527.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当驾驶时看不到画面有明显 delay，不过却需要时间适应后视镜中与后车的距离和平面感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120358-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120358-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120358.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>性能与续航力并备，两个版本同时推出</h3><p>Polestar 4 采用源自吉利集团开发的 SEA 架构，在香港提供两个版本：Long Range Single Motor 配备 200kW（272 匹马力）后驱马达，0-100 公里加速 7.1 秒，续航里程高达 620 公里（WLTP 标准），另外的 Long Range Dual Motor 搭载双马达全轮驱动系统，总输出功率达 400kW（544 匹马力），0-100 公里加速仅需 3.8 秒，续航里程为 590 公里。两个版本均配备 100kWh 的锂电池，支援 200kW 快充技术，由 10% 充至 80% 仅需约 30 分钟，极大提升日常使用便利性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114410-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114410-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114410.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289619" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_113914-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_113914-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_113914.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>短评:，性能强劲操控容易，隔音出色舒适度高</h3><p>今次测试的是马力较强的双马达版本，在 Sport 模式下四驱 544 匹马力绝对能够给予驾驶者超跑级别的加速感，虽然引擎声欠奉但是车箱的隔音却值得一赞，路噪及环境杂声都过滤得非常好，4 Pots Brembo 卡钳的刹车反应及力量亦非常充裕。加上它的悬挂软硬适中，小编在东九龙一带使用 Normal 模式也不会觉得过软，算是偏向舒适的设定但又不失驾驶乐趣和操控性，而且在较高速的弯位 Polestar 4 的低重心设计亦成功把稳定性控制得相当好，高速驾驶亦不失舒适的乘坐感。如果喜欢更接受跑车的操控感，大可以把悬挂及軚盘转向设定为 Firm，相信绝对会有另一番体验！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289638" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120346-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120346-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120346.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>智能科技与豪华内栊</h3><p>Polestar 4 配备多项先进驾驶辅助系统，包括自适应巡航控制（ACC）、车道保持辅助（LKA）、盲点监测（BSM）及 360 度全景摄像头，全面保障驾驶安全。车厢内部展现极简北欧风格，中央配备特大的 15.4 吋的中控屏幕，采用 Android Automotive 作业系统，支援 Google 助理、Google 地图及多款应用程式。数码仪表板、抬头显示器（HUD）以及电子后视镜等高科技配置，驾驶体验更加直觉。座椅方面，Polestar 4 提供高级环保材料，前排座椅具备电动调节及加热功能，后排座椅则可调整椅背角度。此外，车内音响系统采用总输出高达 1400W 的 Harman Kardon 12 喇叭高级音响（Plus Pack 选配），带来更高质素的听觉享受。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120101-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120101-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120101.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289623" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121020-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121020-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121020.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289624" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121001-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121001-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121001.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289625" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120920-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120920-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120920.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289626" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120652-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120652-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120652.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289622" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121029-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121029-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_121029.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲整个车箱的内饰设计走极简路线，中控就只提供一个大班旋转按钮操作音乐播放，其他功能则需要在轻触式中控屏上处理。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289628" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120427-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120427-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_120427.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲后座也有独立的冷气调较及座椅设定，并设有 2 个 type c 充电接口。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114901-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114901-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250124_114901-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>后记: 豪华舒适与出色性能兼备</h3><p>突破传统设计的 Polestar 4 属于 SUV Coupe 车款，同时集合了 SUV 的舒适乘坐体验及 Coupe 跑车的高性能。它取消了传统的后车窗，在改善空气力学之后，更把全景式天窗伸延至车箱更后位置，令整体感觉更加开扬同时提升头部空间。实时的电子后视镜虽然可以提供更广阔的视野，不过驾驶者定必需要一些时间适应。而在动力方面，544 匹双摩打四驱动力加上 590 公里 WLTP 续航对于追求高性能的朋友在香港路面使用肯定绰绰有余。极简设计美学、先进的驾驶科技，同时把高性能与长续航结合，大家又会不会选择 Polestar 4？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/polestaraaaa-694x567.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="567" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/polestaraaaa-694x567.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/polestaraaaa.jpg 804w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
